I really want to go on a safari in Africa, but for that I need $ 3,200 for the trip. It's been 2 years, experiencing such shitty jobs. I did not have any regular income and I waited for something to happen for a year or two.

But I failed at the end of last year, had to quit the job at least to have experience and time to study a new direction. Through recruiting I got an internship in a tech company.

I had only 2 months and I had to pay rent during training, and after that to pay for tickets to attend the conference, and at least for help in the branch office of my country.

Now I am looking for the salary I can pay my trip, where to find work. I'll have to come back with my savings to finish my studies.
